<section class="content reveal">
  <h2>Mission</h2>
  <p>
    Safe DOCX exists to help teams use coding agents for real paperwork workflows, not just code and plaintext files.
    The product focus is deterministic brownfield editing of existing .docx documents where formatting, comments, footnotes,
    and tracked changes must survive automation.
  </p>
  <p>
    We prioritize transparent implementation and trustworthy behavior: local-first execution, open-source code, and
    verifiable test evidence.
  </p>
</section>

