  <h2>How Safe DOCX Helps</h2>
  <p>
    Safe DOCX lets agents edit existing Word documents with predictable results: targeted text updates, paragraph inserts, comments, footnotes, and tracked/clean outputs.
    It is optimized for brownfield .docx work where formatting and review semantics must survive automation.
